@node INTRO "Introduction..."
Introduction...
---------------

   What is this program?!?!?

   Well it is yet another dialling code program.. influenced by the
   excellent Dialling Codes v2.00 by Julian Wright.. And my program borrows
   a couple of things from that program (Including a very similar GUI)

   You are probably wondering why I did this, well the answer is simple.. I
   am a member of a BBS here in the UK that carrys FidoNet.  Well I asked
   fellow users of this BBS what programs they would like, and this was
   requested.. So here it is!!

@endnode

