@node REQUIRE "Do I need a Super Amiga?" 
AmPCS requires:
-------------------
       AmPCS V1.0beta requires the following to run :

   An Amiga (A bit obvious Really)
   Kickstart v2.04+
   Min 300 KB of Memory (varies on size of codes file!)
   Reqtools.Library in Libs:
   Diskfont.library in Libs:
   Xen 8 Font in FONTS:
   a codes file (stdcodes.txt) (UK is Supplied)

@endnode

