                        BBS's.. Look at the planned features :

                      * Converts Archive type to Archive type (lha 2 Lzx or
                        Zip or whatever)

                      * Will convert to ALL known archivers setup in config
                        and automatically keep the smallest archive

                      * Will interface with BBS systems to allow a BBS to
