                        determine whether the file should be deleted (Most
                        only work on the filename)

                      * Allows automatic adding of files to archives

                      * Fully configurable and will run fom a GUI or
                        command line

    AmPCS v2.0        - Improvements will include :

                      * Will allow you to add/delete/edit phone codes
                      * A font-sensitive Gui  
                      * Fully re-sizable window
                      * ANY SUGGESTONS FROM YOU LOT
                      * Printing results out or saving them to a file

